    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document specifies a set of cipher suites for the Transport Security Layer (TLS) protocol to support the Camellia encryption algorithm as a block cipher.  It amends the cipher suites originally specified in RFC 4132 by introducing counterparts using the newer cryptographic hash algorithms from the SHA-2 family.  This document obsoletes RFC 4132. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
